    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><br>Step into the shoes of a Glowie Shooter in a first-person horror shooter where survival is your goal. You must fend off waves of eerie entities who glow in the dark. Also known as &quot;Glowies.&quot; Use your wits, reflexes, and available weapons to survive and get as many as you can.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Face relentless waves of glowies in fast-paced, first-person shooting action. Use your given weapons to keep the glowing menace at bay.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154940/extras/d621b91b569978404354672a26b48c90.poster.avif?t=1725619485\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154940/extras/d621b91b569978404354672a26b48c90.webm?t=1725619485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154940/extras/d621b91b569978404354672a26b48c90.mp4?t=1725619485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>As you eliminate glowies, their numbers and speed increase, making each wave more challenging than the last.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154940/extras/c209ff4ebe1119eb811f11c03fb83c44.poster.avif?t=1725619485\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154940/extras/c209ff4ebe1119eb811f11c03fb83c44.webm?t=1725619485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154940/extras/c209ff4ebe1119eb811f11c03fb83c44.mp4?t=1725619485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Immerse yourself in a chilling environment with eerie soundscapes, dynamic lighting, and spine-tingling visuals.<br><br></li><li>Survive as long as possible against increasingly difficult waves of glowies or better yet, get the required amount of glowies to beat the game. </li></ul><br><br><strong>They are coming. How long can you last?</strong>",
